flowchart TD
    A[Record Expense] --> B[/Enter Expense Details/]
    B --> C[Assign Category]
    C --> D[Attach Receipt]
    D --> E{Link to Project?}

    E -- Yes --> F[Select Project]
    E -- No --> G[No Project Link]

    F --> H{Mark as Billable?}
    G --> H

    H -- Yes --> I[Mark as Billable]
    H -- No --> J[Mark as Non-Billable]

    I --> K[Add to Next Invoice Queue]
    J --> L[Record for Financials/Tax]

    K --> M((Expense Recorded))
    L --> M